# BeatRoute â†’ NSD Integration â€” JSON Format

## Endpoint

```
POST https://never-stop-dreaming-trading.vercel.app/api/integration/orders
```

## Headers

| Header | Value |
|--------|-------|
| `Content-Type` | `application/json` |
| `Authorization` | `Bearer <token>` |

> Token is obtained from the Refresh URL: `https://never-stop-dreaming-trading.vercel.app/api/integration/user/refresh`

---

## JSON Body Format

```json
{
  "retailer_br_id": 15758594,
  "retailer_external_id": "CUST-001",
  "erp_invoice_number": "INV-2026-0001",
  "invoice_date": "2026-03-07",
  "status": 1,
  "order_id": null,
  "external_order_id": null,
  "ship_to_external_id": "",
  "order_status": "Pending",
  "total_tax": 0,
  "total_value": 1500.00,
  "remarks": null,
  "payment_due_date": "2026-03-14",
  "invoice_level_discount": 0,
  "details": [
    {
      "sku_external_id": "SKU-001",
      "quantity": 10,
      "sku_uom": "PC",
      "price_per_item": 100.00,
      "discount_value": 0,
      "gross_value": 1000.00,
      "tax_code": "",
      "tax": 0
    },
    {
      "sku_external_id": "SKU-002",
      "quantity": 5,
      "sku_uom": "PC",
      "price_per_item": 100.00,
      "discount_value": 0,
      "gross_value": 500.00,
      "tax_code": "",
      "tax": 0
    }
  ]
}
```

---

## Field Descriptions

### Order Level (Required)

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| `retailer_br_id` | number | âœ… | BeatRoute retailer ID |
| `erp_invoice_number` | string | âœ… | Invoice number (must be unique â€” duplicates are rejected) |
| `invoice_date` | string | âœ… | Invoice date in `YYYY-MM-DD` format |
| `details` | array | âœ… | Array of line items (at least 1) |

### Order Level (Optional)

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `retailer_external_id` | string | Customer/retailer code |
| `status` | number | Order status code |
| `order_id` | number/null | BeatRoute order ID |
| `external_order_id` | string/null | External order reference |
| `ship_to_external_id` | string | Shipping destination code |
| `order_status` | string | Status name (e.g. "Pending") |
| `total_tax` | number | Total tax amount |
| `total_value` | number | Total order value |
| `remarks` | string/null | Notes or remarks |
| `payment_due_date` | string | Payment due date (`YYYY-MM-DD`) |
| `invoice_level_discount` | number | Invoice-level discount amount |

### Details / Line Items (Required per item)

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| `sku_external_id` | string | âœ… | Product SKU code |
| `quantity` | number | âœ… | Quantity ordered |
| `price_per_item` | number | âœ… | Unit price |

### Details / Line Items (Optional per item)

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `sku_uom` | string | Unit of measure (e.g. "PC", "CS") |
| `discount_value` | number | Discount per line item |
| `gross_value` | number | Gross value (qty Ã— price) |
| `tax_code` | string | Tax code |
| `tax` | number | Tax amount for this item |

---

## Success Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "order_id": "uuid-here",
  "message": "Order created successfully",
  "reference": "INV-2026-0001",
  "total": 1500.00,
  "item_count": 2
}
```

## Error Responses

| Status | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| `400` | Invalid JSON or missing required fields |
| `401` | Invalid or expired token |
| `409` | Duplicate invoice number (already exists) |
| `500` | Server error |
